window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Zara and Lessie return in Book 5 of the Dragon Riders of Elantia series, perfect for fans of Eragon and Pern!</b> <br> <br> When Zara and Lessie finally got their hands on a piece of the Dragon God’s heart, they thought their path was clear. Head to the Forge of Derynnis, gain the death god’s favor, and convince him to destroy the evil relic once and for all. <br> <br> But getting to the Forge is no simple feat, and it’s not even the first thing on Zara’s list. Between battling the Dragon God’s sinister will, evading Salcombe’s sabotage attempts, and securing the future of her people, Zara’s got her work cut out for her. And when she finally reaches the death god’s lair, the price she’ll be forced to pay for his help might just break her.... <br> <br> <i>Scroll up and grab your copy today! </i></p>"; 
